[SN]TITLE[SN]
Accrington Stanley: Chris Eagles and Jonai Donacien join

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Accrington Stanley have signed former Manchester United and Bolton midfielder Chris Eagles as well as former Aston Villa defender Janoi Donacien.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Eagles, 30, who made five appearances for Bury last term, has been training with Stanley but no details about his deal with club have been disclosed.
St Lucia international Donacien, 22, left Aston Villa this summer and has agreed a short-term contract.
Both players are available to face Doncaster in their season opening game.
